</CASEREF>
</CASEHIST>
</CASEREF></P>
<P>On the facts of this case, it was not necessary to decide whether the
Regulation applies only to gift cards purchased as gifts for third parties.</P>
<P><CASEREF CCDBNUM="1716067">
<SOC>Bernstein v. Peoples Trust Co.</SOC>
