</CORRELAT>
<COURTJUR>Ont. S.C.J.</COURTJUR>
</CASEREF>
</CASEHIST>
</CASEREF></P>
<P>The Court held that it was not plain and obvious that prepaid payment cards
were not subject to the Act.</P>
<P><CASEREF CCDBNUM="1868224">
<SOC>Bernstein v. Peoples Trust Company</SOC>
<CITE>2019 ONSC 2867</CITE>
<CORRELAT>
<CITE>2019 CarswellOnt 7328</CITE>
</CORRELAT>
