<FREEFORM>
<P><CASEREF CCDBNUM="1502122">
<SOC>Action Auto Leasing &amp; Gallery Inc. v. Cantlon</SOC>
<JUDGDATE>January 18, 2013</JUDGDATE>
<DOCKET>Doc. SC-12-293</DOCKET>
<CITE>[2013] O.J. No. 212</CITE>
